==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Switching power supply
<hw>Switch"ing power supply</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a device used as
part of an electronic device, which transforms electrical current from
an AC line circuit to DC for use in electronic devices, and which can
use either 110 volt or 220 volt AC line curent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Switchman</ent>⟦br⟧
